list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: of or in agreement with the character or makeup of, or circumstances surrounding, someone or something.

list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: (of a parent or child) related by blood.
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_en: such adopted children always knew who their natural parents were
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: Những đứa trẻ được thông qua như vậy luôn biết cha mẹ tự nhiên của họ là ai

list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: bassoon chơi g-tự nhiên thay vì a-phẳng

an insect or other small creature used as bait, rather than an artificial imitation.
a person born with a learning disability.
